msgstr "But suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows this: "

msgctxt "an10.54:6.2"
msgid "‘lābhīmhi ajjhattaṃ cetosamathassa, lābhī adhipaññādhammavipassanāyā’ti, tena, bhikkhave, bhikkhunā tesuyeva kusalesu dhammesu patiṭṭhāya uttari āsavānaṃ khayāya yogo karaṇīyo. "
msgstr "‘I have both serenity and discernment.’ Grounded on those skillful qualities, they should practice meditation further to end the defilements. "

